Lola Omotayo, the wife of music star, Peter Okoye was a year older last Monday. Her husband and father of her two children, Peter took to Instagram to share some lovely photos of them with the caption: “I’m a rich man because I have a wife with a rich heart. Happy birthday my love @lolaomotayo_okoye. Love you to the moon and back one million times.” Meanwhile, Lola’s age remains a big secret. She only “adds a year” yearly